    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, top, tail and chop your <strong>courgette[s]</strong> into quarters lengthways, then slice finely</p><p>Once the mince has browned, add the <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>courgette</strong> to the pan and cook for 3-4 min further or until the courgette has started to soften</p><p>Reboil half a kettle</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1655811658352-x200.jpg",
