        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve your<strong> beef stock mix </strong>and<strong> harissa paste </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)<strong> </strong>in 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[200ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[250ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your <strong>harissa stock</strong></p><p>Once the courgette has softened, add the <strong>harissa stock</strong> and your <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong> and cook for 10-12 min or until the sauce has thickened to a bolognese-like consistency and the meat is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>harissa pork & beef mince ragù</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1655811662364-x200.jpg",
