            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the pork & beef ragù is cooking, strip your <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems and chop them finely, discard the stems</p><p>Chop your <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Return the <strong>drained potato and carrot </strong>to a low heat<strong> </strong>with <strong>half</strong> your <strong>natural yoghurt</strong>, <strong>half</strong> the <strong>chopped parsley </strong>and<strong> mint </strong>(save the rest for garnish!) and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Mash until smooth – this is your <strong>herby yoghurt & carrot mash</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
