            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>harissa pork & beef mince ragù </strong>with the<strong> herby yoghurt & carrot mash </strong>to the side</p><p>Drizzle over the<strong> remaining natural yoghurt </strong>and sprinkle over the<strong> remaining chopped parsley </strong>and<strong> mint</strong></p><p>Season with a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
